WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:06.592
Hey, good morning family. Thank you for joining me today. Well, there is a lot going on, isn't there?

00:00:06.593 --> 00:00:22.031
The whole Trump tariff thing is really shaking some things up, stirring some things up, and people ask, "Brandon,"through emails and through wherever they are.

00:00:22.032 --> 00:00:27.623
It's been amazing. People are freaked out and asking, "Should we store food?

00:00:27.624 --> 00:00:36.274
Should we buy water? Should we buy guns? Should we do this?"Listen, you should not do anything by watching a video.

00:00:36.275 --> 00:00:51.673
What you should do is pray and ask the Holy Spirit what you should do for your finances and for your life. I told you all I hear in part and I see in part.

00:00:51.674 --> 00:01:10.577
When the things that I see start coming up in the news, I bring the old videos out because I have so many trolls saying that I'm making stuff up, and so I'm just showing, "Hey, I do see stuff and the Lord's showing me these things."And they say, "Are you a prophet?"I say, "No, I'm not a prophet.

00:01:10.578 --> 00:01:25.855
I'm a watchman."I've told you all this. I'm called to pray. And I believe the Lord shows me as a watchman on the wall, looking out on a horizon seeing what's coming towards the camp.

00:01:25.856 --> 00:01:37.388
"Hey, this is what I see coming."And so far there's a lot of accuracy. Have a lot of the things I've seen not come to pass?

00:01:37.389 --> 00:01:41.126
Yes, there's a lot of things that I've seen that have not come to pass yet.

00:01:41.127 --> 00:01:47.202
But the things that I've told you so far—some of those things you've seen in the news.

00:01:47.203 --> 00:01:56.013
So they go, "Well, what's this mean now?"Honestly, I pray none of this that I've seen comes to pass.

00:01:56.014 --> 00:02:17.081
And you can point fingers at me, call me false all day long, and say he's making stuff up or whatever, but I'm here to tell you, we have to pray for what I've seen about China and the trade wars because it's about medical.

00:02:17.082 --> 00:02:28.159
They get so irritated and so frustrated with the escalation of this that they start saying, "We're not giving you medicines and things like that."That's what I saw.

00:02:28.160 --> 00:02:33.919
Now, is that for you to get scared about? No. It could not happen.

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:47.691
If we pray and we ask the Father to intervene in this and pray for these trade wars to deescalate and fall apart and that they come to an agreement, then it's all over. Wouldn't it be?

00:02:47.692 --> 00:03:17.518
I mean, the ultimate goal is not for this to keep going and going and getting out of control and then we go, "Oh, no."Everything I told you—I saw stores that were not able to get merchandise back and forth throughout all the Targets and all the Walmarts and all the Costcos and the Sam's Clubs, and that they had to take everything out of one store and put it in another store because they had to shut that store down because they couldn't get the supplies.

00:03:17.519 --> 00:03:24.594
The things I see, if you look at it in the natural, it will scare you. It will really freak you out.

00:03:24.595 --> 00:03:36.994
But if you keep your eyes on Him, if you keep your eyes vertical and you keep looking at the Father and praying over this stuff, knowing that we have authority, it shouldn't freak you out.

00:03:36.995 --> 00:03:47.111
Now, I have a lot of people all freaked out, and my job right now is I'm diffusing it to say, "Listen, the sky's not falling."Yes, I saw this.

00:03:47.112 --> 00:03:53.039
Yes, what I saw about the trade wars and the things coming. We should pray.

00:03:53.040 --> 00:04:01.308
That's what we're here to do. So, can we change it through prayer? I believe so. All things are possible to him who believes.

00:04:01.309 --> 00:04:05.922
I believe that every believer has the authority of the believer inside of him.

00:04:05.923 --> 00:04:12.925
We have the power and authority that Jesus has given us. That as He is, so are we in this world.

00:04:12.926 --> 00:04:17.728
And if Jesus can cause peace to the storms, we can call peace to the storms.

00:04:17.729 --> 00:04:21.977
We are made in the image of God and we are joint heirs of Jesus Christ.

00:04:21.978 --> 00:04:26.473
And I believe that we can do those things. Some people don't believe it, but I believe we do.

00:04:26.474 --> 00:04:30.807
So if you want to watch me, fine. If you don't want to agree with it, that's on you.

00:04:30.808 --> 00:04:33.947
I know I have all kinds of different beliefs, but I want to tell you this.

00:04:33.947 --> 00:04:41.169
People ask, "Brandon, what are you doing right now? Are you storing up food? Are you doing all this?"No, I'm not.

00:04:41.170 --> 00:04:54.359
I am not getting in fear and going out to the grocery store and buying $10,000 worth of groceries and going, "Well, I've got it all in the garage, and I've got it out here and it's going to get hot in the summer and then next thing I know it's spoiled."I'm not doing that.

00:04:54.360 --> 00:05:07.393
The Holy Spirit didn't tell me, "Brandon, you should go out and buy a freezer full of meat at Sam's tomorrow."He may tell you to do that; He may not.

00:05:07.394 --> 00:05:19.782
But you have to just follow Him for your household. He may say to you, "Go get water. Go get this. Go get that."I don't know where you live.

00:05:19.783 --> 00:05:27.771
I don't know if you live in a major apartment complex with 500 people around you—I have no idea, folks.

00:05:27.772 --> 00:05:41.550
If I lived in Orlando or if I lived in Tampa or a major city that I saw all those people and it's so packed full of people, I might have four or five days'worth of extra food.

00:05:41.551 --> 00:05:53.865
I live in a little bitty town with not a lot of people and a lot around us is farmers—a lot of farmers and a lot of people growing tomato plants and squash in the summer.

00:05:53.866 --> 00:06:08.184
I can go down to the local farmers market and stock up every single week and get fresh vegetables around here with apples—not oranges, but apples—and peaches and pears in the fall and toward the late summer.

00:06:08.185 --> 00:06:12.055
There's all kinds of stuff around here. So, am I freaked out about food?

00:06:12.056 --> 00:06:15.151
No. There's tons of food around here; we have farmers everywhere.

00:06:15.152 --> 00:06:21.409
Now, if I lived in Chicago, it might be a different story. I don't know. But I have to tell you, am I afraid?

00:06:21.410 --> 00:06:26.451
People said, "Should I pull my money out of my bank?"I don't know what you should do.

00:06:26.452 --> 00:06:30.859
All I saw was the things I see and I relay it and I tell you what I see.

00:06:30.860 --> 00:06:36.338
Is that for you? That's for you to pray about. I do not want this stuff I see to come to pass.

00:06:36.339 --> 00:06:43.141
It's like people go, "Well, good for you, Brandon. It came to pass."No, that means it's a prayer fail.

00:06:43.142 --> 00:06:51.723
In my opinion, if I see something that's drastic and I come on here and tell you about it and it happens, we failed.

00:06:51.724 --> 00:06:56.662
Now, I know some of the things we can stop and some of the things we can't.

00:06:56.663 --> 00:07:09.035
I know we are in the last of the last days and I told you we're going to see major things coming, but some of the things I believe we can stop.

00:07:09.036 --> 00:07:19.918
And so that's my main job: to always pray and ask the Father to change it, just like Abraham.

00:07:19.919 --> 00:07:26.719
He came and He told Abraham what He was going to do and they had a conversation about it.

00:07:26.720 --> 00:07:37.137
And if you are a friend of God and you are joint heirs with Him and He comes and talks to you, He'll tell you what He's going to do before He does it.

00:07:37.137 --> 00:07:41.857
Just because we're friends—you tell your wife everything, don't you?

00:07:41.858 --> 00:07:46.075
Usually, if you have a good marriage, or your wife tells her husband everything, right?

00:07:46.076 --> 00:07:54.252
So, the Father, it's like a marriage; we talk and we're friends. And so, that's the way I look at it every day.

00:07:54.253 --> 00:08:04.478
I just go, "Hey, Lord, what's going on today?"Just like I did with New Orleans and the shooting or Trump's ear, the economy crashing afterwards.

00:08:04.479 --> 00:08:09.723
We're seeing those things. It's happening. Do I believe we have a window still?

00:08:09.724 --> 00:08:14.764
People ask, "Brandon, you said we had a window. You said we had a window of four years.

00:08:14.765 --> 00:08:22.396
Where'd that four years go, buddy?"This is what I want to say back to you: it's a four-year window of grace.

00:08:22.397 --> 00:08:34.545
I believe at the end of that four-year window—I don't know, because I'm not going to assume, add to, or take away from anything that He's saying—but a four-year window to me is a four-year window before He comes.

00:08:34.546 --> 00:08:38.777
That's what I have in my heart: that He's getting ready to come that quickly.

00:08:38.778 --> 00:08:41.805
He said it's one last call, and He's leaving the ninety-nine to go after the one.

00:08:41.806 --> 00:08:53.938
He's looking for the sinner in the way-back fields. That's what He's after right now. How long does it take to get all those in? I have no idea.

00:08:53.939 --> 00:09:09.630
People are like, 'We need to get out of here right now.'Listen, North Korea has not been evangelized yet. Has North Korea been radically taught the word of God?

00:09:09.631 --> 00:09:19.728
My son told me there's 40-some million people in North Korea that have never heard—a lot of them have never heard the gospel. Is that fair? No, that's not fair.

00:09:19.729 --> 00:09:28.372
There's a lot of people in China that are still so bound because they're underneath the Iron Curtain that they have not heard yet, and Vietnam and all these other places.

00:09:28.373 --> 00:09:33.195
There's a lot of people that have not had the opportunity to hear the gospel.

00:09:33.196 --> 00:09:37.980
I know that the Lord is the Lord of the harvest, and His heart is for the souls.

00:09:37.981 --> 00:09:44.474
His heart is the harvest. Regardless of what everybody wants—to go, 'Well, I'm tired.

00:09:44.475 --> 00:09:49.720
I'm ready to get out of here'—listen, I want to occupy until He comes.

00:09:49.721 --> 00:09:56.722
So, the four-year window to me is an extension of grace. Will we still see birthing pains? Yes.

00:09:56.723 --> 00:10:07.119
I'm believing—and I told you all I believe when I've prayed and I've heard the Lord—that we will have a wealth transfer laid up for the righteous.

00:10:07.120 --> 00:10:10.414
If you're listening, not everybody's going to participate in this.

00:10:10.415 --> 00:10:16.251
Oh, I don't know. I pray I do. Honest to goodness, you all. Am I qualified for it? I don't know.

00:10:16.252 --> 00:10:23.047
I pray and I ask Him, 'Father, make me right before You that I would be able to be used by You.

00:10:23.048 --> 00:10:57.904
That if You want to give me an idea to get wealth, then Father, to help bring forth the gospel, to do something for Your kingdom, to support people, to help them, then Father, search me and know me.'If I'm not qualified and I mess up, Father, then if it's going to cost me my salvation, if this is going to cost me my marriage, if this is going to cost me my children and we can't handle it, then by all means, Lord, remove that from me because I would rather have nothing than lose my soul to money, to mammon.

00:10:57.905 --> 00:11:09.978
But if He can trust me and He can look at me and say, 'Brandon, okay.'And He said, 'You may not be able to handle a billion dollars, son, or a million dollars.

00:11:09.979 --> 00:11:17.077
I'll give you this.'I don't know. All I know is I seek Him. And as I seek Him, I will find Him.

00:11:17.077 --> 00:11:24.075
The Bible says that, and all the other stuff will be added unto me as I seek Him. And if He sees that I can handle it, fine.

00:11:24.076 --> 00:11:31.835
And if He says, 'Brandon, I need you to plant a big garden this summer in the next couple of days'—I mean, He may tell me.

00:11:31.836 --> 00:11:39.852
I don't know. I'll go out there and say, 'Braden, let's go outside and get the ground till up.'I mean, that's what we'll do.

00:11:39.853 --> 00:11:46.638
I just obey Him. And He may say, 'Brandon, you need to have some cash on hand.

00:11:46.639 --> 00:11:56.344
You may need to have some ones on hand or some fives or some tens or twenties.'I don't know. Whatever He tells you to do, do it.

00:11:56.345 --> 00:12:08.793
I was thinking about when Mary pulled on Jesus and she was putting a mandate on that anointing on His life before it was time.

00:12:08.794 --> 00:12:19.432
And she went to Him and she said, 'Jesus, will you help the bride and bridegroom make the wine?

00:12:19.433 --> 00:12:33.416
Can you help him?'Basically, so He said, 'It's not My time yet.'But her putting a mandate on that anointing that was on His life, knowing who He was, brought it forth and He started walking in it.

00:12:33.417 --> 00:12:43.883
It's putting a demand on the anointing that brings forth the giftings.

00:12:43.884 --> 00:12:50.112
Look what happened to that feast: Jesus showed up and He showed off.

00:12:50.113 --> 00:12:55.177
And I believe as we put a demand on it: 'Father, You are our provider.

00:12:55.178 --> 00:13:02.421
You're Jehovah Jireh.'I believe that You take care of the lilies of the field and the birds of the air.

00:13:02.422 --> 00:13:06.424
How much more will You take care of me as you put a demand on it?

00:13:06.425 --> 00:13:21.555
If He took care of water and turned it into wine, how much more will He? We don't need a drink; maybe all I need is some groceries.

00:13:21.556 --> 00:13:34.685
If Mary could put a mandate on the anointing and pull, and know and believe and stretch out her voice to Him as a mother and say, 'I know You can.

00:13:34.686 --> 00:13:46.575
Will You? Thank you for doing this'—and He's like, 'Out of compassion.'If He had compassion for them, how much more will He have compassion for you?

00:13:46.576 --> 00:13:58.289
Will you just trust Him and say, 'I believe You're going to take care of me in these end times regardless of what I see on the stock market'?

00:13:58.290 --> 00:14:28.472
Regardless of what I see with tariffs, if the Lord tells you to do—remember what Mary turned to the servants and said, 'Whatever He tells you to do, do it.'It was an act of obedience immediately to go and bring forth as she was pulling on it and putting a mandate on it and saying, 'Help us.'Then it was obedience to what He instructed to bring it to pass of what they were believing for.

00:14:28.473 --> 00:14:34.202
And here the wine came and God showed up and showed off. But it was obedience.

00:14:34.203 --> 00:14:40.850
So as we put a mandate on it: 'Father, You're going to take care of us.'I believe it.

00:14:40.851 --> 00:14:44.843
You've got my life. I'm not going to stress out and worry about any of this.

00:14:44.844 --> 00:15:00.534
But if He speaks to you and He says, 'All right, I know I'm going to take care of you, but I want you to go down and put the water in the jugs,'and you say, 'Well, I thought You were just going to show up and show off and do it'—well, just do it.

00:15:00.535 --> 00:15:17.300
Whatever He says to do, do it. Even if it's a can—if He says, 'Billy Joe, I want you to go down to the Walmart store and buy five cans of green beans,'okay, go do it.

00:15:17.301 --> 00:15:27.890
And then all of a sudden, you go in your cupboard and you put those green beans inside there—those five cans—and you open it up the next day and there's thirty cans.

00:15:27.891 --> 00:15:35.962
He's the God of multiplication. He will be the God of the fishes and the loaves to you.

00:15:35.963 --> 00:15:47.112
Well, I only have enough for five cans. It doesn't matter. He had enough to turn the fishes and the loaves and multiply and feed thousands.

00:15:47.113 --> 00:15:54.777
How much more can He do it for you? I refuse to get in fear over all the end-time stuff.

00:15:54.778 --> 00:16:22.744
I refuse to let the circumstances of staying horizontal, looking at things going, 'Man, what are we going to do?'and say, 'No, I take the care out of my prayer and I put my eyes on Jesus regardless of how much I have in my cupboard or my pantry or whatever I've got in my bank account.'If I've got $500 in there and I go, 'Man, all I've got is $500,'God is a God of multiplication.

00:16:22.745 --> 00:16:36.159
I told you the stories that I have that God takes a little bit of nothing and turns it into the fishes and the loaves and we're able to pay our bills for the whole month with eBay and Poshmark.

00:16:36.160 --> 00:16:45.488
We'll get down and we'll go, 'Well, what are we going to do?'Trust God. Trust God.

00:16:45.489 --> 00:16:54.436
And that's what we've done over and over and over and He always comes through.

00:16:54.437 --> 00:17:19.119
I look back at my kids'videos even tonight of what we were like ten years ago when Braden was little, and I wasted so much time worrying and fretting about how I was going to make the electric, how I was going to pay the water bill, how I was going to pay the gas, how I was going to make my car payment.

00:17:19.120 --> 00:17:39.598
I worried so much as a father that it ate me up and drove me always to be in that state of care and that state of worry every single day that it robbed me of their childhood because I wasn't able just to sit back and relax because I was always thinking, 'How am I going to take care of all these kids?

00:17:39.599 --> 00:17:44.554
How am I going to take care of this wife? I don't have an education. I don't have all this.

00:17:44.555 --> 00:17:51.770
What are You going to do for me, Lord?'Oh God, how are you going to take care of me? That was the way it was.

00:17:51.771 --> 00:18:02.973
When Megan was diagnosed and through all the things we’ve had going on, I said, 'Lord, how are you going to do this?'But God has always provided.

00:18:02.974 --> 00:18:08.798
It may not have been as much as I thought I should have, but he always took care of us.

00:18:08.799 --> 00:18:21.592
Even if it wasn't what I really wanted or I didn't get to wear what I wanted, he always took care of me.

00:18:21.593 --> 00:18:33.674
It was just a simple act of trusting. I remember the days when I told you I was excited to find shoes at Payless for the kids.

00:18:33.675 --> 00:18:40.758
You just have to be thankful and walk in the thanksgiving for what he has provided.

00:18:40.759 --> 00:18:48.964
As you walk in thanksgiving and give him glory for everything he has done, he shows up and shows off with more.

00:18:48.965 --> 00:18:57.420
I believe that's where we are. People ask, 'Where are you at, Brandon?'That’s where I’m at.

00:18:57.421 --> 00:19:03.857
I trust God, I stay vertical, and whatever he says to do, do it.

00:19:03.858 --> 00:19:20.479
Just like Mary said, 'Whatever he says to do, do it.'In closing, people said, 'I thought you saw Kim Jong-un removed.

00:19:20.480 --> 00:19:29.157
I thought you said in your last vision you saw a bomb going off on the border.'Yes, I did.

00:19:29.158 --> 00:19:33.897
Kim Jong-un was trying to be buddy-buddy with China and Russia.

00:19:33.898 --> 00:19:55.361
They were trying to bring South Korea into the pact by influencing their government and taking Taiwan back, making a stronger front for China because they're desperate. People say, 'You said you saw Kim Jong-un be removed.

00:19:55.362 --> 00:20:10.779
What happened with that?'I believe God is going to give an opportunity for the North Korean people to find him, so they don't all go to hell because they never heard the gospel.

00:20:10.780 --> 00:20:31.570
I believe God is just and he will bring justice to the injustice, and he will expose and remove Kim Jong-un one day. He will do the same with his sister.

00:20:31.571 --> 00:20:46.158
Just like he did with Pharaoh, he will lead his people out of bondage again and give them a time to hear what the Spirit of the Lord is saying.

00:20:46.159 --> 00:20:57.138
People may not agree, but I believe God is a God of mercy. We are running out of time and coming to the end of things.

00:20:57.139 --> 00:21:07.962
You ask, 'What did you think about the eclipse, Brandon?'I believe it's more than finances. I get caught up in what I say; I’m not the best speaker.

00:21:07.963 --> 00:21:21.626
I go over these videos many times in my mind beforehand because people are mean to me and I try hard to say the right things.

00:21:21.627 --> 00:21:29.110
As I said, I try with the words. Diana often says, 'You meant to say this, Brandon,'when she's sitting next to me.

00:21:29.111 --> 00:21:35.604
She doesn't want to interrupt my flow, but I’d rather she did because I say certain words while meaning something else.

00:21:35.605 --> 00:21:51.032
In my mind, it’s right, but it comes out differently. That’s when people say, 'Well, you said this,'and I realize I didn’t mean it that way.

00:21:51.033 --> 00:22:01.825
If you truly knew me, you'd know I try really hard. I'll say it again, and I hope my son helps me.

00:22:01.826 --> 00:22:22.320
I’ve told him, 'Please correct me if I mess up.'What I saw regarding the eclipse in April happened a year ago.

00:22:22.321 --> 00:22:31.596
That Tuesday, yesterday, was part of a window of opportunity for the shifting of finances.

00:22:31.597 --> 00:22:46.107
He said, 'Pay attention to Israel and Iran in the days ahead.'This is the part I left out.

00:22:46.108 --> 00:22:58.744
People say, 'You messed up on the six-month window.'I was talking about the period from November to April.

00:22:58.745 --> 00:23:12.844
That’s a six-month window. It’s at the end. The Lord said, 'I have been monitoring the hearts.

00:23:12.845 --> 00:23:55.092
I am watching to see how they drink and how they come unto me.'Regarding the river, the Lord told me, 'I'm watching the people who have lost themselves in me.'He said those who are not ashamed of how they drink or how they minister to those on the street corners—those who don't worry about being dignified or flowing a certain way, but are just lapping up the water because they want more of Jesus.

00:23:55.093 --> 00:24:05.279
From the election to where we are now, he’s looking at the heart of America.

00:24:05.280 --> 00:24:15.225
Have the people forgotten what he's already done? Have they let go of the rope?

00:24:15.226 --> 00:24:25.119
He said many have. There is a pride that has set in again. He said, 'They have had stiff necks towards me, Brandon.

00:24:25.120 --> 00:24:29.524
There will be a shaking to awaken, for America will be humbled.

00:24:29.525 --> 00:24:39.520
Through this, I will bring a great revival back to your shores.'How do you get people's attention?

00:24:39.521 --> 00:24:52.290
Through their pocketbooks. Money is America's god, along with the lust of the flesh.

00:24:52.291 --> 00:25:05.538
We have to get soul-driven. I know many of you watching are after souls and want people to come to Jesus. I'm excited you're here because that's what I'm after.

00:25:05.539 --> 00:25:22.043
People ask, 'Where's the revival, Brandon?'I don't know where the full manifestation is yet, but I know it will come out of pressure. He's given us a window.

00:25:22.044 --> 00:25:37.397
I’m believing in an 'all hands on deck'experience where people take this seriously and minister to those in Walmart or wherever they are.

00:25:37.398 --> 00:25:42.042
Not being Bible-beating, but just loving on people and showing the love of God.

00:25:42.043 --> 00:25:53.082
Let’s take communion and pray together. Ask the Father what you should do for your household.

00:25:53.083 --> 00:26:04.453
Don’t act out of fear—don't just rush to buy survival food or a well. Follow the voice of the Lord.

00:26:04.454 --> 00:26:11.316
The Lord said there will be great droughts where we live and that we'll need a well.

00:26:11.317 --> 00:26:21.423
I don’t have a well yet; I priced one and it’s a lot of money. But you believe God; that’s what you do. I don’t freak out.

00:26:21.424 --> 00:26:41.579
I say, 'God, I have a need, so I sow a seed and believe for my harvest.'Lord, you’ll provide a well if you want me to have one.

00:26:41.580 --> 00:26:46.347
I say, 'Lord, this is your bill, not mine.'If you want me to have a well, you’ll provide the well.

00:26:46.348 --> 00:26:53.994
If you want me to have a house in the woods, you'll provide it.

00:26:53.995 --> 00:27:03.172
I'm not going to freak out. You can easily start asking, 'What about this or that?'No.

00:27:03.173 --> 00:27:15.918
Peace. Peace. I ain't doing all that. I'll go find a creek and get a five-gallon bucket of water and boil it if I had to.

00:27:15.919 --> 00:27:21.238
You know what I'm saying? I mean, seriously, I'm an old country boy. I just go out and find an old pond.

